trary to existing models, bats did not display prominent head-scanning behaviors during their final approach, which may be due to constraints of nasal-emitted biosonar for orientation.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Brokaw, Alyson F.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Smotherman, Michael", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/c6786777880caf4316a00d8d07f946db", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/27f7f8db5db74920a6f1b824e93431153a38a33c38e0ae9c59f2804c2e96daab", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/9XWNTPGF", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/9XWNTPGF", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/43420122a3783887350c513f5ee1521f!/b120577-123065", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "4", "pages": "jeb231829", "title": "Journal of Experimental Biology", "volume": "224"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/c6786777880caf4316a00d8d07f946db"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:9XWNTPGF"}, {"identifier": "10.1242/jeb.231829"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "13474767"}}]}}, "titl